org.apache.flume.instrumentation

Interface SinkCounterMBean

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    KafkaSinkCounter, SinkCounter

    public interface SinkCounterMBean
    This interface represents a sink counter mbean. Any class implementing this interface must sub-class MonitoredCounterGroup. This interface might change between minor releases. Please see SinkCounter class.
